author: The Current
description:
John Doe and Exene Cervenka are interviewed at The Current
Support The Current: https://support.mpr.org/youtube  

During a visit to The Current studio, John Doe of the legendary Los Angeles band X responds to a description of public stereotypes about the nature of punk rock.

author: The Current
description:
Watch Amythyst Kiah perform "Silk and Petals" live for The Current
Support The Current: https://support.mpr.org/youtube  

Having broken through with her 2021 album, Wary + Strange, Amythyst Kiah returns with her follow-up, Still + Bright, released on October 25 of this year. While in town for a concert at the Parkway Theater in Minneapolis, Kiah visited The Current studio to play a three-song solo set of songs from Still + Bright.

Watch a performance of "Silk and Petals" above.
